{"type":"answer","id":1249,"parentType":"question","parentId":299,"uid":1029,"contents":"&nbsp;放一个我被知乎续掉的答案吧<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;首先，要一张品味格调很高的茶几，上面要放一些精心装饰的花卉。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n装饰画 是非常必要的，这是寝室艺术修养的体现，大一点的装饰画还能用作壁纸。这里我们选择国画，采用传统的松柏主题，象征中华民族不可战胜的精神，也表达了健康长寿的生活理念<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n地毯是非常提高寝室舒适度的家具，毕竟只住四年那么，有些大学就是水泥地，比较硬一点，那么用地毯就可以赤脚，提高寝室的卫生水平<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n沙发的规格要高，低调不失身份，尤其是白色的盖布。<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n窗帘可以用金色，彰显寝室的规格<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n最后让宿管老师统一着装。那么海派文化的旗袍是不二选择<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/3c6a22a540ed5497c76c1aff4d825e05.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/9905cd99a47595ead87f41261a7d3fbe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/d476b3730a95c7d70ecc27401409a165.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/8d7ba7b7089923940ad0f315308da325.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/87f882242329ab697dbf874bcb982f72.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180503/b867c5532ed2cf9093428765cbc48b8e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-03","agreeCount":58,"discussionCount":0}